cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper proposes a new visual descriptor for pattern recognition using silicon retina cameras, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The descriptor captures spatio-temporal distribution of events, which is relevant to neural networks (cs.NE) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed descriptor is also used as local features in a bag-of-features classification framework, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
